skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: pre series
des:
This skill aims to bring business intelligence to devices belonging to the Amazon Echo family of connected deviecs.

Among its main features are getting aggregate and detailed information about startups, technology areas, investors, patents, rounds of financing, and IPOs.

To start using this skill, just enable it and ask, e.g.:

- Alexa, ask PreSeries how many startups were founded in New York in 2015.

For more use cases and detailed instructions, see our user guide.
